      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014this car is a total dream! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition, honestly looking and driving like it just left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out without a single worry to be found. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new but with a much friendlier price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
