    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated era. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver a linear 333 hp to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucially, the rod bearings, VANOS hub, and rear subframe reinforcement have been proactively completed to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut, retaining its original suspension kinematics and limited-slip differential functionality. With pristine paint depth and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
